{"tid":2405623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟︰香港電台停止轉播BBC節目，令香港在實施《國家安全法》後，權利和自由進一步受侵蝕，「一國兩制」受到削弱的例證","createTime":"2021-02-12T13:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T06:40:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4098504c822ce3f3b18af8e05c69259f27348dcd","tid":2405623,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1575475_1_20210212212238.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1575475_1_20210212212238.jpg&h=8d7ec9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國國家廣播電視總局通報，不允許英國廣播公司BBC世界新聞台繼續在中國境內落地，不受理BBC新一年度落地申請。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟發表聲明，認為這是中國限制言論自由和獲取資訊自由的最新舉措，促敦中國收回決定。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟說，中國做法導致香港電台停止轉播BBC兩個節目，令香港在去年六月實施《國家安全法》後，權利和自由進一步受侵蝕，也是「一國兩制」受到削弱的例證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575475-20210212.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575475-20210212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=9d7800c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575475-20210212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ecb34ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575475-20210212.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://eeas.europa.eu/headquarters/headquarters-homepage/93092/china-statement-spokesperson-bbc-ban_en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feeas.europa.eu%2Fheadquarters%2Fheadquarters-homepage%2F93092%2Fchina-statement-spokesperson-bbc-ban_en&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=f28d8d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eeas.europa.eu/headquarters/headquarters-homepage/93092/china-statement-spokesperson-bbc-ban_en</a>"},{"pid":"f7ac7dae8e9f7b86f49af9212e0208